Package: popReconstructWrappers
Type: Package
Title: Wrappers for Package popReconstruct, Reconstruct Human Populations of the Recent Past
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Mark", "Wheldon", email = "wheldon@un.org", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Wrappers for pacakge popReconstruct which implements the Bayesian hierarchical model described by Wheldon, Raftery, Clark and Gerland (see: <doi:10.1080/01621459.2012.737729>) for simultaneously estimating age-specific population counts, fertility rates, mortality rates and net international migration flows, at the national level.
